HEADWORD: Setwall
<hw>Set"wall`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[CF.
<er>Cetewale</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A plant formerly valued
for its restorative qualities (<spn>Valeriana officinalis</spn>, or
<spn>Valeriana Pyrenaica</spn>).</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>setwal</asp>.]</altsp>
